{
  "stem": "25651.11",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I have to tell you about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's-- that's the story that concerns Mengele and other-- other things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we already had a-- a shock of hair, you know, quite nicely.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were very proud, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It makes you feel really good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he tells me to bend down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now I was-- I-- I-- I was beaten once in Theresienstadt when we weren't working in the gardens.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Theresienstadt, Freddy-- Freddy Hirsch arranged that the youth who were sort of already grown up worked in gardens on the-- on the walls outside Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the produce of the gardens-- you know, fresh produce-- was given to the small children because of vitamin B and all kinds of carrots were grown a lot.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we worked in the gardens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the kids got it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could steal a few carrots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I walked after a day's work in the gardens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had a cap on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And an SS man saw me-- that's in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you're supposed to doff your cap, you see, when you walk past.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I didn't doff my cap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he shouts, come here and gives me one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he says [GERMAN]-- bend down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they have these inch sticks-- walking sticks-- and he'd give you one with the walking stick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wet myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was terribly ashamed that I wet myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all the other boys were very solicitous, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I wet myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I told myself-- you know, he said [GERMAN] to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I told myself, I'm going to hold and I'm not going to wet myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wet myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's-- the bladder has its own mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I got three.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other boy-- and I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I recognized him as.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
